Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Recorder and Ransell OAD #02 Start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竖笛与双肩书包
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.03,0:00:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 下次再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是在这里打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 要来喝杯橙汁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我叫宫川淳志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 来面试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等健哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那家伙介绍来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天能上班么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:45.77,Ttile,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(677,542)}淳\N志\N和\N酒\N保
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始看一下工作的内容就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一直在盯着这边看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳志 你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.45,0:01:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我在这看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长 他是未成年的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 说起来也没问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你几岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学五年级
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个有趣的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫淳志君来着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很明白我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边酒的种类很多 店里的人也很帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是警察的木岛姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫川君？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 负责人在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能让小学生在酒吧工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是那家伙的玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都不像小学生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学生这种时间还在外面是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 店长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我跟健哥问好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健哥打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以妨碍人家工作啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健哥又开始新的工作了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健哥很帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教了我很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 能做久就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正月回去就吵着问还不结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得同学有联络还是请我去婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦卡伦的30年陈酿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错啊 我也是30年的旧货啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(529,642)}等一下 前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是运动短裤世代 不穿运动短裤穿什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中裤啊 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装什么装啊 是短裤啊短裤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 前辈 我都不知道你在说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来干不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份工作
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theme
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:03:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高鳴る鼓動を目印に　夜明けが迫る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始まりの合図　Let's go!　Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲かせた恋は夢花火　出会えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑って 意気揚々 Fly me to your eyes
